  "detailed_description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1819520/extras/4aa16d2a1e09d2d783c16d178846db67.poster.avif?t=1657894324\" width=610 height=322 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1819520/extras/4aa16d2a1e09d2d783c16d178846db67.webm?t=1657894324\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1819520/extras/4aa16d2a1e09d2d783c16d178846db67.mp4?t=1657894324\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1819520/extras/739a1bef4af4a5669f9f02cc10ea2f7d.avif?t=1657894324\" width=610 height=90 /></span><br>Constellation is a transformative relationship with constellations and puzzles, to discover something that only the stars hold. Take a comfy spot and enjoy this experience!<br><br>Increase mindfulness, concentration and focus through a conversation with the stars. Evade yourself from everyday life as you build constellations in the sky.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1819520/extras/Preview_2.gif?t=1657894324\" /></span><br><br>Constellations is a meditative, minimalist puzzle game about finding patterns in the stars. In each level, connect the stars without the lines crossing and slowly fill the sky with constellations. Explore a starmap full of carefully designed levels with diverse mechanics, or go to the black hole to play endless puzzles.<br><br>Stars, constellations and figures can be found as main elements: Stars reveal the way to reach a sky completely made up of constellations. Some constellations reveal incredible pictures.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1819520/extras/1165ce57cabce361c1a70fa5a7a3a982.poster.avif?t=1657894324\" width=610 height=322 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1819520/extras/1165ce57cabce361c1a70fa5a7a3a982.webm?t=1657894324\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1819520/extras/1165ce57cabce361c1a70fa5a7a3a982.mp4?t=1657894324\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1819520/extras/8cf2ad5720eb3b2577500189c95d7666.avif?t=1657894324\" width=610 height=71 /></span><br>- Simple and intuitive puzzle mechanics for all ages.<br>- Polished controls for a satisfying experience.<br>- Meditative astronomic chill visuals and music.<br>- Solidly designed campaign with over 100 levels with varied mechanics.<br>- Level generator with infinite combinations.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1819520/extras/922f953d63980f3cd80e199b2d0dfc2c.poster.avif?t=1657894324\" width=610 height=322 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1819520/extras/922f953d63980f3cd80e199b2d0dfc2c.webm?t=1657894324\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1819520/extras/922f953d63980f3cd80e199b2d0dfc2c.mp4?t=1657894324\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
